0.title: Latency
0.query:
timeseries { avg(network.latency), value.A = avg(network.latency, scalar: true) }, by: { thousandeyes.source.agent.name }, filter: { matchesValue(thousandeyes.source.agent.name, { $Agents }) AND matchesValue(thousandeyes.test.name, { $Tests }) AND matchesValue(thousandeyes.stream.id, { $StreamId }) }
| limit 20

subQueries.filter: thousandeyes.source.agent.name in ($Agents) AND thousandeyes.test.name  in ($Tests) AND thousandeyes.stream.id in ($StreamId )
